I was confused to see this showing up again, but I think it's fascinating. That said, I would call Addendum C a big mistake. I love  I'd rather see the note about Llao and go look that up myself to find out what the explanation is. I mean, up until that point, it's this neat thing where it causes crazy weather, which is bad on a number of levels, but is apparently also keeping something worse from getting into the lake. It's tantalizing, and knowing what it's about ruins the mystery.

Also, I'd suggest taking the reference to Pangloss out of Addendum B, just leave it in the note. And maybe even make that the last addendum, the punchline to the whole thing. Novote for now, but you're on the right track.







